messages.message: This run of mine has 28 failed tests. I’ve re-run this PR about 10 times now and there’s no real consistent failures happening. Is this when I just get someone to force merge a PR? https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/10037/overview?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1
the latest run looks like it failed due to the sandbox issue on uploading files, but the previous runs idk
i think in this case it'd be fine to force merge, but i'd keep an eye on similar failures; we've seen the human review tests in the penultimate run (10033) been flaky in the past few days
(@Udit i think tried to make them less flaky but something something clicks not going through?)
right on, appreciate taking you taking a look
This looks like the issue where you need to delete the sandbox and rerun the tests
